---
title: Homestyle Crustless Turkey Pot Pie with Sour Cream Mashed Potatoes
description: Get ready for all the comfy-cozy flavors of chicken pot pie, served over creamy mashed potatoes! You'll sizzle chicken with carrot, scallion, garlic, and thyme, then swirl in butter and flour. Once your "pot pie filling" is thick and bubbly, you'll spoon it all over sour cream mashed potatoes and, voila—a hearty, warming meal in a quick 30 minutes.
